'''飓风威拉'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Willa}}）是2018年10月下旬在墨西哥西南部产生狂风暴雨并造成重大破坏的强劲[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，其中[[锡那罗亚州|锡那罗亚州]]和[[纳亚里特州|纳亚里特州]]灾情特别严重。威拉是[[2018年太平洋颶風季|2018年太平洋颶風季]]形成的第25个热带气旋，第22个获命名的风暴，第13场飓风，第十场大型飓风，和追平历史最高纪录的第三场[[五级太平洋飓风列表|五级飓风]]，还是[[2006年太平洋颶風季|2006年]][[2006年飓风莱恩|飓风莱恩]]过后首场[[登陸_(氣象學)|登陆]]锡那罗亚州的大型飓风。

威拉源自10月初离开非洲的[[东风波|东风波]]，14日抵达[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]西南部后，[[國家颶風中心|美国国家飓风中心]]认为系统有组织成热带气旋的潜力并开始监控，但东风波实际上没有显著发展便穿越[[中美洲|中美洲]]进入东太平洋。气象机构继续追踪，系统于10月20日在[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]西南近海组织成热带低气压，而且当天就升级成热带风暴威拉并开始[[快速增强|快速增强]]，次日达到[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时260公里的最高强度，已属五级飓风。受[[眼牆置換循環|眼牆置換循環]]和风切变增多的共同影响，气旋逐渐减弱，于10月24日清晨以三级飓风强度登陆墨西哥錫那羅亞州，此后迅速弱化，当天便在墨西哥东北部上空逐渐消散。

面对飓风威胁，墨西哥西部地区接获[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴或飓风观察预警和警告]]。气旋共夺走九条人命，经济损失达161亿[[墨西哥比索|墨西哥比索]]（相当于同年的8.25亿[[美元|美元]]）{{#tag:ref|如无特别说明，所有金额均为2018年币值<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis | title = Mexico / U.S. Foreign Exchange Rate | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | url = https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/DEXMXUS | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200827010253/https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/DEXMXUS | archive-date = 2020-08-27 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。|group="注"}}，其中大部分发生在飓风沿途地区。威拉共导致四个州近十万居民家中断电，[[埃斯奎纳帕德伊达尔戈|埃斯奎纳帕]]的学校、医院和基础设施遭受重大破坏，损失总额估计达60亿墨西哥比索（合3.06亿美元）。河流泛滥成灾导致建筑受损，锡那罗亚州和纳亚里特州大片地区没有饮用水。周边多个州发生洪灾和山体滑坡，造成破坏和人员受伤。威拉的残留后来进入美国，在[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]引发山洪。飓风过后，大批灾民直到数月后才获得[[墨西哥联邦政府|墨西哥联邦政府]]的直接援助。该国居民主要依靠救灾组织帮助搜寻个人财物，修复受损房屋。锡那罗亚州政府向灾民提供的床垫已经腐烂，联邦政府用于救灾的拨款下落不明，部分地区直到风暴过去数月后才开始重建。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Willa 2018 track.png}}
飓风威拉源自2018年10月2日离开[[非洲|非洲]]西海岸的[[东风波|东风波]]，此后几天向西穿越大西洋，其间[[对流|对流]]（即[[雷暴|雷暴]]）偶有爆发，但在强烈的[[风切变|风切变]]干扰下无法朝中心聚集<ref name="TCR">{{cite report | first = Michael | last = Brennan | publisher = [[國家颶風中心|National Hurricane Center]] | date = 2019-04-02 | accessdate = 2020-09-22 | title = Hurricane Willa | series = Tropical Cyclone Report | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP242018_Willa.pdf | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200911051430/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP242018_Willa.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2020-09-11 | format = PDF}}</ref>。10月14日，[[國家颶風中心|美国国家飓风中心]]开始监控位于[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]西南部的东风波，认为系统有发展成热带天气系统的潜力<ref>{{cite report | first = Stacy | last = Stewart | title = Five-Day Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook: 200 PM EDT, Sun Oct 14 2018 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/xgtwo/gtwo_archive.php?current_issuance=201810141734&basin=atl&fdays=5 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-09-22 | date = 2018-10-14 | archive-date = 2020-09-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200924080054/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/xgtwo/gtwo_archive.php?current_issuance=201810141734&basin=atl&fdays=5 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。次日，行进至[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]东南方向的系统结构已有改善，而且陆地附近的外界条件也有利于进一步发展，[[美国空军预备役司令部|美国空军预备役司令部]][[第53气象侦察中队|第53气象侦察中队]]为此制订[[洛克希德WC-130侦察机|洛克希德WC-130侦察机]]飞入系统调查的计划<ref>{{cite report | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/xgtwo/gtwo_archive.php?current_issuance=201810151736&basin=atlc&fdays=2 | title = Two-Day Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook: 2:00 pm EDT, Mon Oct 15 2018 | first = Eric | last = Blake | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2018-10-15 | access-date = 2020-09-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181021111553/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/xgtwo/gtwo_archive.php?current_issuance=201810151736&basin=atlc&fdays=2 | archivedate = 2018-10-21 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。但是，东风波于10月16日[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]][[伯利兹|伯利兹]]，故而无法继续组织<ref>{{cite report | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/xgtwo/gtwo_archive.php?current_issuance=201810161121&basin=atlc&fdays=2 | title = Two-Day Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook: 8:00 am EDT, Tue Oct 16 2018 | first = Stacy | last = Stewart | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2018-10-16 | access-date = 2020-09-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181021111541/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/xgtwo/gtwo_archive.php?current_issuance=201810161121&basin=atlc&fdays=2 | archivedate = 2018-10-21 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

10月17日清晨，东风波进入东太平洋<ref>{{cite report | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/xgtwo/gtwo_archive.php?current_issuance=201810171031&basin=epac&fdays=2 | title = Two-Day Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook: 11:00 pm PDT, Tue Oct 16 2018 | first = David | last = Zelinsky | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2018-10-17 | accessdate = 2020-09-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181021111552/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/xgtwo/gtwo_archive.php?current_issuance=201810171031&basin=epac&fdays=2 | archivedate = 2018-10-21 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，次日仍未凝聚成热带气旋，结构渐趋混乱，形状显著拉长<ref>{{cite report | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/xgtwo/gtwo_archive.php?current_issuance=201810181740&basin=epac&fdays=2 | title = Two-Day Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook: 11:00 am PDT, Thur Oct 18 2018 | first = Robbie | last = Berg | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2018-10-18 | accessdate = 2020-09-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181021111547/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/xgtwo/gtwo_archive.php?current_issuance=201810181740&basin=epac&fdays=2 | archivedate = 2018-10-21 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。10月19日清晨，东风波所在位置东侧形成新[[低壓槽|低壓槽]]<ref>{{cite report | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/xgtwo/gtwo_archive.php?current_issuance=201810182355&basin=epac&fdays=2 | title = Two-Day Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook: 5:00 pm PDT, Thu Oct 18 2018 | first = David | last = Zelinsky | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2018-10-28 | accessdate = 2020-09-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190327091616/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/xgtwo/gtwo_archive.php?current_issuance=201810182355&basin=epac&fdays=2 | archivedate = 2019-03-27 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，并于当天组织成[[2018年热带风暴维森特|热带风暴维森特]]<ref>{{Cite report | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep23/ep232018.discus.002.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Vicente Discussion Number 2 | first = Robbie | last = Berg | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2018-10-19 | access-date = 2020-09-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190506165550/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep23/ep232018.discus.002.shtml | archivedate = 2019-05-06 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。原本的东风波继续向西并逐渐组织，于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]10月20日午夜0点在[[曼萨尼约|曼萨尼约]]以南约425公里海域发展成热带低气压<ref name="TCR" />。气旋中心以南开始形成[[雨带|带状特征]]，中心以东的云顶温度低至零下85至91摄氏度<ref>{{cite report | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.001.shtml? | title = Tropical Depression Twenty-Four-E Discussion Number 1 | first = Stacy | last = Stewart | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2018-10-20 | accessdate = 2020-09-22 | archive-date = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200923170416/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.001.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。接下来系统发展出紧密的内核<ref>{{cite report | first = Robbie | last = Berg | title = Tropical Storm Willa Discussion Number   2 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.002.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-09-22 | date = 2018-10-20 | archivedate = 2018-10-21 | deadurl = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181021111555/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.002.shtml }}</ref>，美国国家飓风中心于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}中午12点左右将曼萨尼约西南偏南方向约465公里洋面的热带低气压升级成热带风暴，并以“威拉”（{{lang|en|Willa}}）命名<ref name="TCR" />。

