不久，风暴开始[[快速增强|快速增强]]，下层中心嵌入环流中心周围的[[中心密集雲團區|中心密集雲團區]]下方，还开始沿中层[[高壓脊|高壓脊]]的西侧边缘转朝西北方向前进<ref name="d3">{{cite report | accessdate = 2020-09-22 | archivedate = 2018-10-21 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.003.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Willa Discussion Number 3 | first = Robbie | last = Berg | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2018-10-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181021111603/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.003.shtml | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。气旋四周及上空的条件有利于发展，风切变很少，空气湿度高，[[海面温度|海面温度]]达到29摄氏度<ref>{{cite report | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.004.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Willa Discussion Number 4 | first = John | last = Cangialosi | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2018-10-21 | accessdate = 2020-09-22 | archivedate = 2019-02-28 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190228191909/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.004.shtml}}</ref>，促使威拉于{{lang|en|UTC}}10月21日早上六点升级成飓风<ref name="TCR" />。系统周围的[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]格局良好，对流中心形成小[[風眼|風眼]]<ref>{{cite report | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.005.shtml? | title = Hurricane Willa Discussion Number 5 | first = Stacy | last = Stewart | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2018-10-21 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181021151350/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.005.shtml | archivedate = 2018-10-21 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}下午18点，气旋已达[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风风力等级|三级飓风]]标准，[[红外线|红外线]]图像和[[卫星影像|卫星]]图像上的风眼都已非常清晰，成为[[2018年太平洋颶風季|2018年太平洋颶風季]]第十场大型飓风<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="Disc 8">{{cite report | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.008.shtml? | title = Hurricane Willa Discussion Number 8 | first = John | last = Cangialosi | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2018-10-21 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | archive-date = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200923170416/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.008.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。风暴继续快速增强，于{{lang|en|UTC}}10月22日早上六点左右在墨西哥[[哈利斯科州|哈利斯科州]][[科连特斯角|科连特斯角]]（{{lang|en|Cabo Corrientes}}）西南偏南方向约315公里水域达到[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时260公里，最低气压925[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，27.3[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度，已属五级飓风，这也表明威拉的风力时速在48小时内共提升205公里<ref name="TCR" />{{#tag:ref|[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]当时认为威拉的风力时速经过48小时共提升195公里，此时尚未达到最高强度，只是接近五级标准<ref>{{cite report | first = Stacy | last = Stewart | title = Hurricane Willa Discussion Number   9 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-22 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.009.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archive-date = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200923170417/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.009.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但经之后重新分析调整风暴达到最高强度的时间，得到上述结果<ref name="TCR" />。|group="注"|name="Willa Intensification Rate"}}。此后几天气旋蜿蜒逼近墨西哥，沿高压脊边缘转向北上，后又因中到上层低压槽逼近转朝东北方向移动<ref name="Disc 8" /><ref name="Disc 16">{{cite report | first = Lixion | last = Avilia | title = Hurricane Willa Discussion Number  16 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.016.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-24 | archive-date = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200923170429/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.016.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

威拉达到最高强度后不久，微波卫星图像发现外层风眼墙，表明飓风进入[[眼牆置換循環|眼牆置換循環]]<ref name="d10">{{cite report | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.010.shtml? | title = Hurricane Willa Discussion Number 10 | first = Daniel | last = Brown | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2018-10-22 | access-date = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181022232646/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.010.shtml | archivedate = 2018-10-22 | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.public.010.shtml? | title = Hurricane Willa Public Advisory Number 10 | first = Daniel | last = Brown | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2018-10-22 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181023160439/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.public.010.shtml | archivedate = 2018-10-23 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。在此期间，气旋还同东南方向的小型热带风暴维森特相互影响<ref name="Vicente discussion 14">{{cite report | last = Pasch | first = Richard | title = Tropical Storm Vicente Discussion Number  14 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep23/ep232018.discus.014.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center  | date = 2018-10-23 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190506165556/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep23/ep232018.discus.014.shtml | archivedate = 2019-05-06 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。虽然外界环境有利，但眼牆置換循環仍令威拉减弱，风眼被云层遮挡<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite report | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.011.shtml? | title = Hurricane Willa Discussion Number 11 | first = Daniel | last = Brown | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2018-10-22 | access-date = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801094448/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.011.shtml | archivedate = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。随着西南向风切变开始增长，风暴强度在{{lang|en|UTC}}10月23日早上六点左右回落到三级飓风范围<ref>{{Cite report | archivedate = 2018-10-23 | deadurl = yes | date = 2018-10-23 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.014.shtml? | title = Hurricane Willa Discussion Number 14 | first = Daniel | last = Brown | publisher = National Hurricane Center | access-date = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181023234258/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.014.shtml }}</ref>。眼牆置換循環结束后，飓风停止减弱，风眼于{{lang|en|UTC}}下午17点45分经过圣胡安尼托岛和[[瑪麗亞群島|瑪麗亞群島]]上空<ref name="TCR" />。{{lang|en|UTC}}10月24日凌晨1点20分，系统以三级飓风强度从[[錫那羅亞州|錫那羅亞州]]棕榈佛得角（{{lang|es|Palmito del Verde}}）附近[[登陸_(氣象學)|登陆]]，此时的一分钟持续风速为每小时185公里，中心最低气压968毫巴（百帕，28.6英寸汞柱）<ref name="TCR" />。威拉至此成为2015年[[颶風派翠莎|颶風派翠莎]]过后首场袭击墨西哥的太平洋大型飓风，也是[[2006年飓风莱恩|2006年飓风莱恩]]过后第一场吹袭锡那罗亚州的大型飓风<Ref>
{{cite web | author = Jeff Masters | title = A Hyperactive 2018 Eastern Pacific Hurricane Season Ends | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200212145416/https://www.wunderground.com/cat6/Hyperactive-2018-Eastern-Pacific-Hurricane-Season-Ends | archivedate = 2020-02-12 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-11-28 | url = https://www.wunderground.com/cat6/Hyperactive-2018-Eastern-Pacific-Hurricane-Season-Ends | publisher = Weather Underground }}
</ref>。风暴朝内陆进发，风眼很快就从卫星图像上消失<ref name="Disc 16" />。受西南向风切变和墨西哥山区地形共同影响，威拉迅速减弱，{{lang|en|UTC}}早上六点已消退成热带风暴<ref name="TCR" />，并且六小时后便在墨西哥东北部上空消散，中到上层环流与下层环流分离<ref>{{cite report | first = Stacy | last = Stewart | title = Tropical Depression Willa Discussion Number  17 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-24 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.017.shtml? | archive-date = 2020-09-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200924080055/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2018/ep24/ep242018.discus.017.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。气旋残留继续向东北方向移动，在美国多个州产生降水<ref name="TCR" />，残留低气压蕴藏的能量还促使美国东部形成[[东北风暴|东北风暴]]<ref>{{cite news | title = A Look at the Excessive Rainfall from Hurricane Willa in Mexico and Texas | url = https://www.weathernationtv.com/news/a-look-at-the-excessive-rainfall-from-hurricane-willa-in-mexico-and-texas/ | work = WeatherNation | first = Mace | last = Michaels | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191111205316/https://www.weathernationtv.com/news/a-look-at-the-excessive-rainfall-from-hurricane-willa-in-mexico-and-texas/ | archive-date = 2019-11-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

