{{lang|en|UTC}}10月21日下午15点，[[墨西哥联邦政府|墨西哥政府]]向[[納亞里特州|納亞里特州]][[圣布拉斯_(纳亚里特州)|圣布拉斯]]（{{lang|en|San Blas}}）至[[馬薩特蘭|馬薩特蘭]]的该国西岸地区发布[[熱帶氣旋警告|飓风观察预警]]，同时向圣布拉斯至普拉亚普鲁拉（{{lang|en|Playa Perula}}）之间发布热带风暴观察预警。六小时后，马萨特兰至坦培瓦亚湾间（{{lang|en|Bahia Tempehuaya}}）地区也收到热带风暴观察预警。{{lang|en|UTC}}10月22日凌晨三点，飓风观察预警和热带风暴观察预警升级成飓风警告或热带风暴警告。威拉在[[杜蘭戈州|杜蘭戈州]]上空减弱成热带风暴后，所有警告均于{{lang|en|UTC}}10月24日早上六点中止。<ref name="TCR" />

威拉逼近墨西哥太平洋沿海地区期间，该国还接获其他多种天气预警。风暴直接威胁的[[锡那罗亚州|锡那罗亚州]]和[[纳亚里特州|纳亚里特州]]地区收到代表最高危险等级的红色警报<ref name="Economic">{{cite news | first = Blanca Estela | last = Regalado López | title = Alerta roja en Sinaloa, inminente impacto del Huracán Willa | url = https://www.debate.com.mx/mexico/willa-huracan-mazatlan-alerta-roja-sinaloa-nayarit-20181023-0067.html | work = Debate | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801021838/https://www.debate.com.mx/mexico/willa-huracan-mazatlan-alerta-roja-sinaloa-nayarit-20181023-0067.html | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="Evac Number">{{cite news | title = Nayarit en alerta roja por huracán ‘Willa’ | url = https://www.diariodemexico.com/nayarit-en-alerta-roja-por-huracan-willa | work = Diario de México | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200911041507/https://www.diariodemexico.com/nayarit-en-alerta-roja-por-huracan-willa | archive-date = 2020-09-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。锡那罗亚州中部和哈利斯科州[[巴亚尔塔港|巴亚尔塔港]]接到代表高危险等级的橙色警报<ref>{{cite news | title = Alerta naranja en Puerto Vallarta, por los efectos de Willa | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200518152602/https://noticieros.televisa.com/videos/alerta-naranja-en-puerto-vallarta-por-los-efectos-de-willa/ | work = Noticieros Televisa | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-23 | deadurl = no | url = https://noticieros.televisa.com/videos/alerta-naranja-en-puerto-vallarta-por-los-efectos-de-willa/ | archivedate = 2020-05-18 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Alerta Naranja En Sinaloa Por Huracán Willa | url = https://www.tvazteca.com/aztecanoticias/alerta-naranja-en-sinaloa-por-huracan-willa/3301761 | work = TV Azteca | accessdate = 2019-08-01 | archivedate = 2019-08-01 | date = 2018-10-23 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801021848/https://www.aztecanoticias.com.mx/alerta-naranja-en-sinaloa-por-huracan-willa/3301761 }}</ref>。[[奇瓦瓦州|奇瓦瓦州]]大部分地区进入黄色警戒状态，表明中等程度危险，危胁主要是暴雨<ref>{{cite news | title = Chihuahua activa alerta amarilla por lluvias de "Willa" | url = https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/chihuahua-activa-alerta-amarilla-lluvias-willa/ | work = Noticieros Televisa | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-24 | archive-date = 2020-05-29 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200529140622/https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/chihuahua-activa-alerta-amarilla-lluvias-willa/ }}</ref>。[[南下加利福尼亞州|南下加利福尼亞州]]因海岸沿岸的海浪威胁收到绿色预警，代表最低等级危险。墨西哥海军部长[[维达尔弗朗西斯科·索伯伦·桑斯|维达尔弗朗西斯科·索伯伦·桑斯]]（{{lang|es|Vidal Francisco Soberón Sanz}}）海军上将在索诺拉州、锡那罗亚州、纳亚里特州、哈利斯科州、科利马州和米却肯州启动致力军事防灾救灾的海洋计划预防措施<ref>{{cite news | title = En 6 estados, Marina activa fase de prevención por 'Willa' | url = https://www.milenio.com/estados/6-marina-activa-fase-prevencion-willa | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | work = Milenio | date = 2018-10-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174544/https://www.milenio.com/estados/6-marina-activa-fase-prevencion-willa | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。[[科蒙都|科蒙都港]]、[[拉巴斯_(南下加利福尼亚州)|拉巴斯港]]、[[洛斯卡沃斯|洛斯卡沃斯港]]及其他位于[[加利福尼亚湾|加利福尼亚湾]]和科尔特斯海的港口禁止小型船只出海<ref>{{cite web | title = Alerta Verde en BCS por Willa; habrá estas restricciones | url = https://www.unotv.com/noticias/estados/baja-california-sur/detalle/alerta-verde-en-bcs-por-willa-habra-estas-restricciones-123376/ | work = Uno TV | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801021840/https://www.unotv.com/noticias/estados/baja-california-sur/detalle/alerta-verde-en-bcs-por-willa-habra-estas-restricciones-123376/ | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。锡那罗亚州[[康科迪亚自治区|康科迪亚]]（{{lang|es|Concordia}}）、[[科萨拉自治区|科萨拉]]（{{lang|es|Cosalá}}）、[[伊洛塔|伊洛塔]]（{{lang|es|Elota}}）、[[埃斯奎纳帕自治区|埃斯奎纳帕]]、[[马萨特兰自治区|马萨特兰]]（{{lang|es|Mazatlán}}）、[[罗萨里奥自治区|罗萨里奥]]（{{lang|es|Rosario}}）和[[圣伊格纳西奥自治区|圣伊格纳西奥自治区]]（{{lang|en|San Ignacio}}）停课<ref>{{cite news | title = Se suspenden clases por huracán “Willa” en Sinaloa | url = https://noticieros.televisa.com/videos/se-suspenden-clases-por-huracan-willa-en-sinaloa/ | work = Noticieros Televisa | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-21 | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801055125/https://noticieros.televisa.com/videos/se-suspenden-clases-por-huracan-willa-en-sinaloa/ }}</ref>。哈利斯科州北岸和南岸约有1265所学校关闭<ref name="Jalisco class">{{cite news | title = Huracán Willa: Al menos 2.500 personas son llevadas a refugios en Jalisco | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | url = https://elcomercio.pe/mundo/mexico/huracan-willa-2-500-personas-reubicadas-jalisco-mexico-noticia-nndc-570584-noticia/?ref=ecr | work = El Comercio | date = 2018-10-23 | archive-date = 2020-09-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200924080116/https://elcomercio.pe/mundo/mexico/huracan-willa-2-500-personas-reubicadas-jalisco-mexico-noticia-nndc-570584-noticia/?ref=ecr | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Jalisco Class II">{{cite news | title = Desalojan comunidades y vigilan carreteras de Jalisco por huracán ‘Willa’ | url = https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/desalojan-comunidades-vigilan-carreteras-jalisco-huracan-willa/ | work = Noticieros Televisa | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190821033109/https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/desalojan-comunidades-vigilan-carreteras-jalisco-huracan-willa/ | archive-date = 2019-08-21 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

锡那罗亚州和纳亚里特州约有20万人离开家园<ref name="Evac Number" />，其中约四万人<ref>{{cite news | first = Eél María | last = Angulo | title = México: el huracán Willa toca tierra en Sinaloa | url = https://www.france24.com/es/20181024-mexico-huracan-willa-evacuacion-inundaciones | work = France 24 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-24 | archive-date = 2019-04-21 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190421202153/https://www.france24.com/es/20181024-mexico-huracan-willa-evacuacion-inundaciones }}</ref>经墨西哥陆军、海军及应急人员协助安置在2900多个避难所。风暴沿途商铺和企业关闭，[[马萨特兰国际机场|马萨特兰国际机场]]及附近酒店风暴期间暂停开放。<ref name="evac">{{cite news | first = Karina | last = Suárez | title = Willa deja 13.000 evacuados y severos daños materiales a su paso por México | date = 2018-10-25 | newspaper = El País | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | archive-date = 2019-04-21 | deadurl = no | url = https://elpais.com/internacional/2018/10/23/actualidad/1540304377_617181.html | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190421185756/https://elpais.com/internacional/2018/10/23/actualidad/1540304377_617181.html }}</ref>。面对洪灾威胁，马萨特兰自治区30个社区疏散<ref>{{cite news | title = Estas son las colonias que serán evacuadas en Mazatlán | url = https://www.debate.com.mx/sinaloa/huracan-willa-colonias-evacuadas-mazatlan-20181022-0133.html | website = Debate | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-22 | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174619/https://www.debate.com.mx/sinaloa/huracan-willa-colonias-evacuadas-mazatlan-20181022-0133.html }}</ref>。应急部门将沿海城市超过4250人强制疏散，并在风暴来袭前建立58个避难所<ref>{{cite web | first = Alba | last = Moraleda | title = Willa se disipa en el noroeste de México tras tocar tierra anoche en Sinaloa con categoría 3 | website = Telemundo | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | url = https://www.telemundo.com/noticias/noticias-telemundo/willa-se-disipa-en-el-noroeste-de-mexico-tras-tocar-tierra-anoche-en-sinaloa-con-categoria-tmna2992214 | date = 2018-10-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190421201157/https://www.telemundo.com/noticias/2018/10/23/willa-se-disipa-en-el-noroeste-de-mexico-tras-tocar-tierra-anoche-en-sinaloa-con | archive-date = 2019-04-21 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。哈利斯科州设立23个避难所，约2500人提前转移<ref>{{cite news | title = Huracán ‘Willa’ se degrada a tormenta tropical | url = https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/huracan-willa-se-degrada-tormenta-tropical/ | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | work = Noticieros Televisa | date = 2018-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191102191235/https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/huracan-willa-se-degrada-tormenta-tropical/ | archive-date = 2019-11-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Luna | first = Adriana | title = Instalan 23 refugios temporales en costa de Jalisco por ‘Willa’ | url = https://www.excelsior.com.mx/nacional/instalan-23-refugios-temporales-en-costa-de-jalisco-por-willa/1273390 | work = Excelsior | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801021841/https://www.excelsior.com.mx/nacional/instalan-23-refugios-temporales-en-costa-de-jalisco-por-willa/1273390 | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。飓风促使[[埃斯奎纳帕德伊达尔戈|埃斯奎纳帕]]至少六千人撤离<ref>{{cite news | title = Desalojan a 6 mil habitantes de Escuinapa, Sinaloa, por ‘Willa’ | archive-date = 2019-08-02 | deadurl = no | url = https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/clima-sinaloa-hoy-23-octubre-2018-desalojan-6-mil-habitantes-escuinapa-willa/ | work = Noticieros Televisa | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190802093920/https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/clima-sinaloa-hoy-23-octubre-2018-desalojan-6-mil-habitantes-escuinapa-willa/ }}</ref>。墨西哥自然灾害救济机构“丰登”（{{lang|en|Fonden}}）提前向风暴登陆点附近及预计路线沿途居民分配90[[公噸|公噸]]食品<ref name="90 tons">{{cite news | last = Sánchez | first = Irene | title = Declaran zona de desastre a Escuinapa y Rosario, en Sinaloa | url = https://www.jornada.com.mx/ultimas/estados/2018/11/01/declaran-zona-de-desastre-a-escuinapa-y-rosario-en-sinaloa-2946.html | work = La Jornada | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174546/https://www.jornada.com.mx/ultimas/estados/2018/11/01/declaran-zona-de-desastre-a-escuinapa-y-rosario-en-sinaloa-2946.html | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。飓风登陆前数小时，墨西哥海军在[[南下加利福尼亚州|南下加利福尼亚州]][[拉巴斯_(南下加利福尼亚州)|拉巴斯]]设立粮食和其他物资收集中心<ref>{{cite news | title = 2da Zona Naval instala centro de Acopio en apoyo a damnificados de Sinaloa por "Willa" | url = https://www.diarioelindependiente.mx/2018/10/2da-zona-naval-instala-centro-de-acopio-en-apoyo-a-damnificados-de-sinaloa-por-willa | work = Diario El Independiente | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174545/https://www.diarioelindependiente.mx/2018/10/2da-zona-naval-instala-centro-de-acopio-en-apoyo-a-damnificados-de-sinaloa-por-willa | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

面对飓风威拉和热带风暴维森特的双重威胁，[[诺唯真极乐号|诺唯真极乐号]]（''{{lang|en|Norwegian Bliss}}''）游轮于10月23日改道[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[聖地牙哥_(加利福尼亞州)|聖地牙哥]]<ref>{{cite news | last = Saunders | first = Mark | title = Tropical storms force Norwegian Bliss cruise ship to divert to San Diego | url = https://www.10news.com/news/tropical-storms-force-norwegian-bliss-cruise-ship-to-divert-to-san-diego | publisher = KGTV San Diego | accessdate = 2020-09-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190421204322/https://www.10news.com/news/tropical-storms-force-norwegian-bliss-cruise-ship-to-divert-to-san-diego | archive-date = 2019-04-21 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。不过，墨西哥国有的[[墨西哥石油公司|墨西哥石油公司]]宣布会在哈利斯科州、锡那罗亚州、纳亚里特州、索诺拉州和科利马州维持正常运营<ref>{{cite news | title = Pemex anuncia medidas de prevención por huracán Willa | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174555/https://www.contrareplica.mx/nota-pemex-anuncia-medidas-de-prevencion-por-huracan-willa2018221018 | website = Contra Replica | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-22 | url = https://www.contrareplica.mx/nota-pemex-anuncia-medidas-de-prevencion-por-huracan-willa2018221018 }}</ref>。为防万一，锡那罗亚州暂停所有公共交通和生产经营活动<ref name="Economic" />。纳亚里特州的公路和企业关闭，政府官员呼吁居民留在家里<ref name="Evac Number" />。为防抽水设备风暴期间损坏，纳亚里特州[[特皮克|特皮克]]的27个社区于10月23日停水<ref>{{cite news | title = Suspenden servicio de agua en 27 colonias de Tepic por Willa | url = https://www.debate.com.mx/mexico/suspenden-agua-potable-27-colonias-tepic-nayarit-huracan-willa-20181023-0163.html | work = Debate | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174541/https://www.debate.com.mx/mexico/suspenden-agua-potable-27-colonias-tepic-nayarit-huracan-willa-20181023-0163.html | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。哈利斯特州交通运输部聘请四百人检视322座桥梁和超过2200公里长的公路。该机构还备有包括[[鏟斗機|鏟斗機]]在内的60台机器，准备应对山体滑坡。风暴期间，待命的路勤人员从22人增至40人。<ref name="Jalisco Class II" />

== 影响 ==

=== 墨西哥 ===
[[File:Flooding_Along_the_Nueces_River.jpg|thumb]]泛滥成灾的照片]]

气旋风眼从[[瑪麗亞群島|瑪麗亞群島]]的两个岛屿上空经过，产生时速179公里的强烈阵风，15分钟的平均持续风速达每小时142公里，相当于时速160公里的一分钟持续风速<ref name="TCR" />。玛丽亚群岛监狱在风暴期间受损，棕榈树被连根拔起，屋顶坍塌，栅栏上的铁丝网也被扯落<ref>{{cite news | title = Así era la vida de los presos que se niegan a dejar las Islas Marías | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.debate.com.mx/mexico/Asi-era-la-vida-de-los-presos-que-se-niegan-a-dejar-las-Islas-Marias-20190401-0088.html | work = Debate | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2019-04-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801021840/https://www.debate.com.mx/mexico/Asi-era-la-vida-de-los-presos-que-se-niegan-a-dejar-las-Islas-Marias-20190401-0088.html }}</ref>。

据[[追風_(惡劣氣候)|追风者]]记载，飓风风眼登陆墨西哥本土时的最低气压只有968毫巴（百帕，28.6英寸汞柱]]），表明登陆时的风速为每小时185公里。登陆点及移动路线周边的阵风达飓风强度，同时伴随大浪和强烈的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]。墨西哥西部降下暴雨，降水最多的圣安德烈斯米尔皮拉斯（{{lang|en|San Andrés Milpillas}}）位于纳亚里特州北部，雨量达391毫米；哈利斯科州西部的[[锡瓦特兰|锡瓦特兰]]也测得335毫米雨量。除上述两州外，威拉还在科利马州、杜蘭戈州、[[米却肯州|米却肯州]]和锡那罗亚州产生强降水。<ref name="TCR" />受风暴影响，锡那罗亚州、 纳亚里特州、杜蘭戈州和米却肯州约有9.62万人失去供电<ref name="evac" />。

==== 锡那罗亚州 ====
飓风威拉在锡那罗亚州登陆，埃斯奎纳帕和罗萨里奥两个自治区与外界的交通中断<ref name="los">{{cite news | title = Huracán Willa deja sin luz y agua a varias comunidades de Sinaloa y provoca daños carreteros | date = 2018-10-24 | url = https://www.animalpolitico.com/2018/10/danos-huracan-willa-sinaloa/ | publisher = Animal Politico | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200911063026/https://www.animalpolitico.com/2018/10/danos-huracan-willa-sinaloa/ | archive-date = 2020-09-11 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-09-23 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | url = https://www.accuweather.com/en/weather-news/in-case-you-missed-it-willa-fuels-flooding-in-southern-us-joins-noreaster-mysterious-rectangular-iceberg-discovered-in-antarctica/342378 | title = In Case You Missed It: Willa Fuels Flooding in Southern US, Joins Nor'easter; Mysterious Rectangular Iceberg Discovered in Antarctica | last = Galimberti | first = Katy | date = 2019-07-02 | work = AccuWeather | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | archive-date = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200923170453/https://www.accuweather.com/en/weather-news/in-case-you-missed-it-willa-fuels-flooding-in-southern-us-joins-noreaster-mysterious-rectangular-iceberg-discovered-in-antarctica/342378 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。狂风令民房受损，还刮倒树木阻塞道路。埃斯奎纳帕综合医院受到破坏，部分屋顶和墙壁坍塌，军人将院内35名病人转移。<ref>{{cite news | last = Ibarra | first = Aarón | title = Deja ‘Willa’ daños en hospital, apagones e inundaciones en Escuinapa | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200321143201/https://riodoce.mx/2018/10/23/deja-willa-danos-en-el-hospital-apagones-e-inundaciones-en-escuinapa/ | work = Ríodoce | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-23 | deadurl = no | url = https://riodoce.mx/2018/10/23/deja-willa-danos-en-el-hospital-apagones-e-inundaciones-en-escuinapa/ | archive-date = 2020-03-21 }}</ref>该市的电力和饮用水供应中断<ref name="evac" />，估计损失总额达60亿[[墨西哥比索|墨西哥比索]]（合3.06亿美元）<ref name="Willa Damage 1" />。埃斯奎纳帕72所学校因飓风严重受损，罗萨里奥也有19所<ref name="90 tons" />，全州七个自治区共有1.7万公顷庄稼受到破坏<ref>{{cite news | last = Bustamante | first = Jesús | title = Frío también pega a hectáreas de cultivos en Sinaloa | url = https://www.excelsior.com.mx/nacional/frio-tambien-pega-a-hectareas-de-cultivos-en-sinaloa/1288086 | work = Excelsior | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2019-02-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174540/https://www.excelsior.com.mx/nacional/frio-tambien-pega-a-hectareas-de-cultivos-en-sinaloa/1288086 | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

