in-aterrizar-aun-apoyos-por-el-huracan-willa-el-fonden-busca-nuevo-recuento-de-danos/ | work = Ríodoce | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2019-06-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200922223839/https://riodoce.mx/2019/06/25/sin-aterrizar-aun-apoyos-por-el-huracan-willa-el-fonden-busca-nuevo-recuento-de-danos/ | archive-date = 2020-09-22 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，约三千公顷农作物因河水泛滥受损<ref>{{cite news | last = Quintero | first = Pedro | title = Willa ocasiona una catástrofe en la agricultura y ganadería | url = https://www.debate.com.mx/sinaloa/sinaloa/danos-huracan-willa-sector-agricola-rosario-sinaloa-20181027-0003.html | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | work = Debate | date = 2018-10-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174625/https://www.debate.com.mx/sinaloa/sinaloa/danos-huracan-willa-sector-agricola-rosario-sinaloa-20181027-0003.html | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。暴雨在[[馬薩特蘭|馬薩特蘭]]引发岩崩，卡马隆（{{lang|es|Camarón}}）泻湖水位上涨<ref name="Support">{{cite news | last = Toxqui | first = Angélica | title = Deja huracán Willa sólo daños menores en Mazatlán, Sinaloa | url = https://acustiknoticias.com/2018/10/deja-huracan-willa-solo-danos-menores-en-mazatlan-sinaloa/ | work = Acustik Noticias | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731171327/https://acustiknoticias.com/2018/10/deja-huracan-willa-solo-danos-menores-en-mazatlan-sinaloa/ | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

