威拉在纳亚里特州共造成至少100亿墨西哥比索（合5.1亿美元）的经济损失<ref>{{cite news | last = Vargas | first = Gustavo | url = https://www.ntv.com.mx/2018/11/05/polo-dominguez-danos-en-nayarit-por-willa-podrian-ser-de-10-mil-millones-de-pesos/ | title = Polo Domínguez: Daños en Nayarit por Willa podrían ser de 10 mil millones de pesos | work = NTV | date = 2018-11-11 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190421115441/https://www.ntv.com.mx/2018/11/05/polo-dominguez-danos-en-nayarit-por-willa-podrian-ser-de-10-mil-millones-de-pesos/ | archive-date = 2019-04-21 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="Nayarit Water">{{cite web | last = Gutierritos | first = Jefferson | title = El Desastre Aún No Termina: Hay Riesgo De Una Emergencia Sanitaria En Nayarit | url = https://www.sopitas.com/noticias/desastre-riesgo-emergencia-sanitaria-nayarit/ | work = Sopitas | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-11-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801134344/https://www.sopitas.com/noticias/desastre-riesgo-emergencia-sanitaria-nayarit/ | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，导致约十万人无家可归<ref name="Nayarit bankrupt">{{cite news | last1 = Tello | first1 = Antonio | last2 = Madrigal | first2 = Guadalupe | title = Gobierno de Nayarit se declara en bancarrota para atender emergencia por ‘Willa’ | url = https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/gobierno-de-nayarit-se-declara-en-bancarrota-para-atender-emergencia-por-willa/ | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | work = Noticieros Televisa | date = 2018-11-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190814062527/https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/gobierno-de-nayarit-se-declara-en-bancarrota-para-atender-emergencia-por-willa/ | archive-date = 2019-08-14 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，共12个自治区进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]<ref name="milen" />。单该州北部的农业水力系统就受到价值七亿墨西哥比索（合3570万美元）的破坏<ref>{{cite news | first = Victor | last = Rochín | url = https://tvpacifico.mx/noticias/220445-estiman-danos-en-red-hidroagricola-en-el-norte-por-mas-de-de-700-millones-de-pesos | title = Estiman daños en red hidroagrícola en el norte, por mas de de 700 millones de pesos | date = 2018-10-30 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | work = Televisoras del Pacífico | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190417000000/https://tvpacifico.mx/noticias/220445-estiman-danos-en-red-hidroagricola-en-el-norte-por-mas-de-de-700-millones-de-pesos | archive-date = 2019-04-17 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。暴雨令河水浪头涨至超过11米，迫使多个自治区人员疏散<ref name="milen">{{cite news | last = Reza | first1 = Abraham | last2 = Arellano | first2 = Salvador | title = Se desbordan ríos en Nayarit por 'Willa' | url = https://www.milenio.com/estados/lluvias-willa-provocan-desbordamiento-rios-nayarit | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | work = Milenio | date = 2018-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174542/https://www.milenio.com/estados/lluvias-willa-provocan-desbordamiento-rios-nayarit | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，全州共1.2万人被迫前往避难所<ref name="Televisa Acaponeta">{{cite news | title = Nayarit en emergencia por desbordamiento de ríos tras “Willa” | url = https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/nayarit-emergencia-desbordamiento-rios-tras-willa/ | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | work = Noticieros Televisa | date = 2018-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801055123/https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/nayarit-emergencia-desbordamiento-rios-tras-willa/ | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

飓风降下暴雨，在[[圣佩德罗梅斯基塔河|圣佩德罗河]]（{{lang|en|San Pedro River}}）与[[阿卡波內塔河|阿卡波內塔河]]沿线引发重大洪灾，18万人受影响<ref name="univision nov1">{{cite news | last = Cacelín | first = Janet | title = Fotos: Una semana después del paso del huracán Willa, 180,000 personas en Nayarit aún sufren los efectos de las inundaciones | url = https://www.univision.com/noticias/desastres-naturales/fotos-una-semana-despues-del-paso-del-huracan-willa-180-000-personas-en-nayarit-aun-sufren-los-efectos-de-las-inundaciones-fotos | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | work = Univision | date = 2018-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801134344/https://www.univision.com/noticias/desastres-naturales/fotos-una-semana-despues-del-paso-del-huracan-willa-180-000-personas-en-nayarit-aun-sufren-los-efectos-de-las-inundaciones-fotos | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。圣佩德罗河沿线四人溺毙，其中[[华吉科里|华吉科里]]（{{lang|en|Huajicori}}）三人，[[图斯潘_(纳亚里特州)|图斯潘]]（{{lang|en|Tuxpan}}）的圣维森特（{{lang|es|San Vicente}}）一人<ref name="nay25">{{cite news | first = Karina | last = Cancino | title = Cuatro muertos y 150 mil damnificados por paso de 'Willa' en Nayarit | date = 2018-10-25 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | work = El Financiero | url = https://www.elfinanciero.com.mx/nacional/cuatro-muertos-y-150-mil-damnificados-por-paso-de-willa-en-nayarit | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200917162234/https://www.elfinanciero.com.mx/nacional/cuatro-muertos-y-150-mil-damnificados-por-paso-de-willa-en-nayarit | archive-date = 2020-09-17 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。唯一通往乌卡拉山谷社区的公路被洪水冲毁，居民同外界的联系中断。狂风和洪水令当地养虾场血本无归，其中一户农民损失的虾有20至30公吨，价值约两百万墨西哥比索（合8.2万美元）。<ref name="Shrimp">{{cite news | title = Nayarit no se recupera tras el paso de ‘Willa’; 180 mil habitantes siguen incomunicados | url = https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/nayarit-no-se-recupera-tras-el-paso-de-willa-180-mil-habitantes-siguen-incomunicados/ | work = Noticieros Televisa | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200408083910/https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/nayarit-no-se-recupera-tras-el-paso-de-willa-180-mil-habitantes-siguen-incomunicados/ | archive-date = 2020-04-08 | deadurl = no}}</ref>圣佩德罗河位于图斯潘境内河段溢出，导致污水泄露，该自治区四所公立学校中有三所遭受洪灾严重破坏，纳亚里特州还有另外42所学校受到相当程度破坏<ref>{{cite news | last = Torres | first = Raúl | title = Concentran ayuda en Tuxpan, Nayarit, tras huracán Willa | url = https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/concentran-ayuda-en-tuxpan-nayarit-tras-huracan-willa | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | work = El Universal | date = 2018-11-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801135845/https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/concentran-ayuda-en-tuxpan-nayarit-tras-huracan-willa | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。图斯潘数万居民遭受深达两米的洪水影响<ref name="Tuxpan flood">{{cite news | last = Moya | first = Ricardo | title = Damnificados por "Willa" siguen removiendo escombros; buscan refugio | archive-date = 2020-05-27 | url = https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/damnificados-por-willa-siguen-removiendo-escombros-buscan-refugio | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | work = El Universal | deadurl = no | date = 2018-11-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200527095645/https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/damnificados-por-willa-siguen-removiendo-escombros-buscan-refugio}}</ref>。纳亚里特州北部还因河流泛滥导致饮用水短缺<ref name="Shrimp" />，供水直到风暴过去至少两周才陆续恢复<ref name="Nayarit Water" />。图斯潘政府的粮仓被淹，两吨食品援助毁于一旦<ref name="ladobe">{{cite news | last = Nuño | first = Analy S. | title = El naufragio de Nayarit, entre la ayuda civil y el gobierno ausente | url = https://ladobe.com.mx/2018/11/el-naufragio-de-nayarit-entre-la-ayuda-civil-y-el-gobierno-ausente/ | accessdate = 2020-9-23 | work = LadoB | date = 2018-11-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801134347/https://ladobe.com.mx/2018/11/el-naufragio-de-nayarit-entre-la-ayuda-civil-y-el-gobierno-ausente/ | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。消防员通宵达旦救助被困屋顶的灾民<ref>{{cite news | title = Rescatan a hombre arrastrado por río en Nayarit | url = https://www.informador.mx/mexico/Rescatan-a-hombre-arrastrado-por-rio-en-Nayarit-20181025-0076.html | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | work = El Informador | date = 2018-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801134343/https://www.informador.mx/mexico/Rescatan-a-hombre-arrastrado-por-rio-en-Nayarit-20181025-0076.html | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

阿卡波內塔河沿线洪灾严重程度创下新纪录，洪峰高达12.2米，最大泄洪量为每秒1.7万立方米，[[阿卡波内塔|阿卡波内塔]]受到严重影响。墨西哥68号联邦公路许多车辆被洪水所困，阿卡波内塔收费站附近情况特别严重。民防及墨西哥海军人员开展至少80次水陆救援。<ref name="Televisa Acaponeta" />[[墨西哥15D号联邦公路|墨西哥15D号联邦公路]]位于阿卡波內塔至拉瓜西马（{{lang|es|La Guásima}}）路段因洪水封闭<ref>{{cite news | title = Cerrada Autopista Villa Unión- Tepic por daños del huracán Willa | url = https://www.noroeste.com.mx/publicaciones/view/cerrada-autopista-villa-union-tepic-por-danos-del-huracan-willa-1145912 | accessdate = 2020-03-18 | work = Noroeste | date = 2018-10-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174546/https://www.noroeste.com.mx/publicaciones/view/cerrada-autopista-villa-union-tepic-por-danos-del-huracan-willa-1145912 | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。

==== 其他地区 ====
威拉在米却肯州降下暴雨，部分地区发生洪灾<ref name="train" />，导致河流泛滥。科因齐奥（{{lang|es|Cointzio}}）大坝达到九八成容量，州首府[[莫雷利亚|莫雷利亚]]的蓄水和排污系统全部满荷。首府部分地点水深达一米，致使40个社区被淹，成百上千的民宅进水。贾卡兰达斯（{{lang|en|Jacarandas}}）社区的污水系统发出异味，居民被迫转移。全市共开设三个避难所容纳灾民，<ref>{{cite news | title = Huracán Willa inunda Morelia | archive-date = 2020-02-15 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.cronica.com.mx/notas/2018/1098238.html | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200215121000/http://www.cronica.com.mx/notas/2018/1098238.html | work = La Crónica de Hoy}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Gutierritos | first = Jefferson | title = Morelia está literalmente bajo el agua por el huracán "Willa" | url = https://www.sopitas.com/noticias/morelia-literalmente-bajo-agua-huracan-willa/ | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | work = Sopitas | date = 2018-10-23 | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801134351/https://www.sopitas.com/noticias/morelia-literalmente-bajo-agua-huracan-willa/}}</ref><ref name="morrr">{{cite news | title = Activan Plan DN-III por lluvia e inundación en Morelia, Michoacán | date = 2018-10-22 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | work = Noticieros Televisa | url = https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/clima-michoacan-hoy-22-octubre-2018-lluvias-causan-inundacion-morelia/ | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200320100634/https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/clima-michoacan-hoy-22-octubre-2018-lluvias-causan-inundacion-morelia/ | archive-date = 2020-03-20 | deadurl = no}}</ref>经济损失估计为3500万墨西哥比索（合179万美元）<ref name="Willa Damage 2" />。阿塔帕诺（{{lang|en|Atapaneo}}）因山体滑坡导致货运列车脱轨，两人因此受伤<ref name="train">{{cite news | title = Willa provoca inundaciones en Morelia e impactará en Sinaloa como categoría 3 | url = https://www.animalpolitico.com/2018/10/willa-lluvias-morelia-sinaloa/ | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | work = Animal Politico | date = 2018-10-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190417000005/https://www.animalpolitico.com/2018/10/willa-lluvias-morelia-sinaloa/ | archive-date = 2019-04-17 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="morrr" />。风暴带来的雨水令[[查帕拉湖|查帕拉湖]]上涨<ref>{{cite news | work = Reporte Indigo | title = No todo es destrucción… Willa provoca ‘milagro’ en el Lago de Chapala | date = 2018-10-23 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.reporteindigo.com/reporte/no-todo-es-destruccion-willa-provoca-milagro-en-el-lago-de-chapala/ | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801021838/https://www.reporteindigo.com/reporte/no-todo-es-destruccion-willa-provoca-milagro-en-el-lago-de-chapala/}}</ref>。

威拉在[[科利馬州|科利馬州]]沿海引起的大浪将船掀翻，船上分别28岁和30岁的两兄弟遇溺，两人当时正在抛洒亲人的骨灰，尸体后由地方官员和墨西哥海军找回<ref>{{cite news | last = Martínez | first = Abraham Acosta | title  =Van a Colima a esparcir cenizas de familiar, mueren por oleaje de ‘Willa’ | url = https://www.excelsior.com.mx/nacional/van-a-colima-a-esparcir-cenizas-de-familiar-mueren-por-oleaje-de-willa/1273163 | work = Excelsior | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200911051906/https://www.excelsior.com.mx/nacional/van-a-colima-a-esparcir-cenizas-de-familiar-mueren-por-oleaje-de-willa/1273163 | archive-date = 2020-09-11 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。威拉和附近的热带风暴维森特导致天气反复无常，停靠[[曼萨尼约|曼萨尼约]]和图斯潘的许多[[油輪|油輪]]无法卸油，再加上向[[瓜达拉哈拉_(墨西哥)|瓜达拉哈拉]]运送[[石油|石油]]的主要管道关闭，导致[[哈利斯科州|哈利斯科州]]燃料短缺，约500个加油站受影响<ref>{{cite news | first = Patricia | last = Romo | url = https://www.eleconomista.com.mx/estados/Persiste-desabasto-de-gasolina-en-Jalisco-20181104-0096.html | title = Persiste desabasto de gasolina en Jalisco | work = El Economista | date = 2018-11-04 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190417000029/https://www.eleconomista.com.mx/estados/Persiste-desabasto-de-gasolina-en-Jalisco-20181104-0096.html | archive-date = 2019-04-17 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

附近的哈利斯科州同样降下暴雨，引发街道洪灾，河流泛滥。[[圣帕特里西奥_(哈利斯科州)|梅拉克]]（{{lang|es|Melaque}}）的[[步兵|步兵]]总部被淹，军人被迫转移。急流冲破[[拉曼萨尼拉|拉曼萨尼拉]]（{{lang|en|La Manzanilla}}）鳄鱼栖息地的篱笆，成百上千的鳄鱼逃脱。<ref>{{cite news | title = ‘Willa’ deja cocodrilos sueltos en Barra de Navidad, Jalisco | date = 2018-10-24 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | work = Noticieros Televisa | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190821033111/https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/clima-jalisco-willa-deja-cocodrilos-sueltos-barra-de-navidad/ | archive-date = 2019-08-21 | deadurl = no | url = https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/clima-jalisco-willa-deja-cocodrilos-sueltos-barra-de-navidad/}}</ref>大量降水令[[帕帕洛阿潘河|帕帕洛阿潘河]]与[[夸察夸尔科斯河|夸察夸尔科斯河]]泛滥成灾<ref>{{cite news | title = Rios de Mexico Reviven Peligrosamente… El Papaloapan Y Coatzacoalcos Comienzan A Desbordarse | url = https://www.reporteindigo.com/reporte/rios-de-mexico-reviven-peligrosamente-el-papaloapan-y-coatzacoalcos-comienzan-a-desbordarse/ | work = Reporte Indigo | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801021838/https://www.reporteindigo.com/reporte/rios-de-mexico-reviven-peligrosamente-el-papaloapan-y-coatzacoalcos-comienzan-a-desbordarse/ | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。蓬塔佩鲁拉（{{lang|es|Punta Pérula}}）的洪水有60厘米高，至少十余幢房屋进水。[[巴亚尔塔港|巴亚尔塔港]]近海波涛汹涌，当地还有树木倒塌并发生山体滑坡。<ref name="Jalisco class" />暴雨在索諾拉州[[諾加萊斯_(索諾拉州)|諾加萊斯]]夺走两条人命，洪水卷走汽车并冲进民房和商铺<ref>{{cite news | title = ‘Willa’ pega en Sinaloa y deja 2 muertos en Sonora | work = Milenio | date = 2018-10-25 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | url = https://www.milenio.com/estados/willa-pega-sinaloa-deja-2-muertos-sonora | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200912205702/https://www.milenio.com/estados/willa-pega-sinaloa-deja-2-muertos-sonora | archive-date = 2020-09-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

杜蘭戈州梅斯基特自治区（{{lang|en|Mezquital Municipality}}）一名电力工人暴雨期间触电后摔死<ref>{{cite news | date = 2018-10-25 | title = Trabajador de CFE muere electrocutado producto de las lluvias por 'Willa' | accessdate = 2019-08-01 | work = Tribuna | url = https://www.tribuna.com.mx/mexico/Trabajador-de-CFE-muere-electrocutado-producto-de-las-lluvias-por-Willa-20181025-0074.html | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801021837/https://www.tribuna.com.mx/mexico/Trabajador-de-CFE-muere-electrocutado-producto-de-las-lluvias-por-Willa-20181025-0074.html | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。该州至少有五个城镇被淹，[[新城自治区_(杜兰戈州)|新城自治区]]（{{lang|en|Pueblo Nuevo Municipality}}）发生山崩，导致十个乡村社区的35幢民居受损<ref>{{cite news | title = Huracán 'Willa' deja daños en Durango | url = https://www.elsiglodetorreon.com.mx/noticia/1511947.huracan-willa-deja-danos-en-durango.html | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | work = El Siglo de Torreón | date = 2018-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200215120958/https://www.elsiglodetorreon.com.mx/noticia/1511947.huracan-willa-deja-danos-en-durango.html | archive-date = 2020-02-15 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。10月23至24日，[[墨西哥40号联邦公路|墨西哥40号联邦公路]]位于[[杜兰戈|杜兰戈]]至马萨特兰间部分路段封闭，全州各地学校停课至10月25日<ref name="Durango Dam">{{cite news | title = Willa ocasiona diversas afectaciones en Durango | url = https://www.elsoldemexico.com.mx/republica/sociedad/willa-ocasiona-diversas-afectaciones-en-durango-2282881.html | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | work = El Sol de Mexico | date = 2018-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200216050249/https://www.elsoldemexico.com.mx/republica/sociedad/willa-ocasiona-diversas-afectaciones-en-durango-2282881.html | archive-date = 2020-02-16 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Tras paso de 'Willa' reabren la carretera Durango - Mazatlán | url = https://www.milenio.com/estados/abren-circulacion-super-carretera-durango-mazatlan | work = Milenio | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | date = 2018-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174707/https://www.milenio.com/estados/abren-circulacion-super-carretera-durango-mazatlan | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[萊爾多_(杜蘭戈州)|萊爾多]]的经济损失约为1.4亿墨西哥比索（合714万美元）<ref name="Willa Damage 3" />。面对不断上涨的水位，圣埃琳娜（{{lang|es|Santa Elena}}）大坝周边地区共有两百人撤离<ref name="Durango Dam" />。

威拉和附近的热带风暴维森特在[[伊達爾戈州|伊達爾戈州]]降下暴雨，共引发十起山体滑坡。瓦斯特克（{{lang|es|Huasteca}}）和塞拉（{{lang|es|Sierra}}）的公路被石块和树枝堵塞。[[萨夸尔蒂潘|萨夸尔蒂潘]]（{{lang|es|Zacualtipán}}）有两人因遭遇山体滑坡入院治疗，[[卡尔纳里|卡尔纳里]]（{{lang|en|Calnali}}）的山崩掩埋房屋，七人被迫转移。<ref>{{cite news | title = Deja lluvia vías con bloqueos y dos lesionados en Hidalgo | url = https://criteriohidalgo.com/noticias/hidalgo/deja-lluvia-vias-con-bloqueos-y-dos-lesionados-en-hidalgo | accessdate = 2020-09-16 | work = Criterio Hidalgo | date = 2018-10-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200103180051/https://criteriohidalgo.com/noticias/hidalgo/deja-lluvia-vias-con-bloqueos-y-dos-lesionados-en-hidalgo | archive-date = 2020-01-03 | deadurl = no}}</ref>韦韦特拉（{{lang|es|Huehuetla}}）和[[特南戈山谷|特南戈山谷]]（{{lang|es|Tenango del Valle}}）的道路也因山体滑坡无法通行。其他受山崩影响的公路包括：特兰奇诺（{{lang|en|Tlanchinol}}）至韦亚帕（{{lang|en|Hueyapa}}）州级公路位于特佩瓦坎德格雷罗（{{lang|es|Tepehuacán de Guerrero}}）境内路段，[[帕丘卡|帕丘卡]]至韦胡特拉（{{lang|en|Huejutla}}）公路位于[[小米内拉尔|小米内拉尔]]（{{lang|es|Mineral del Chico}}）境内路段，以及[[墨西哥城|墨西哥城]]至[[坦皮科|坦皮科]]的联邦公路。<ref>{{cite news | title = Van 10 desgajamientos por lluvias en Hidalgo; afectan carreteras y vialidades | url = https://heraldodemexico.com.mx/estados/van-10-desgajamientos-por-lluvias-en-hidalgo-afectan-carreteras-y-vialidades/ | newspaper = El Heraldo de México | accessdate = 2020-09-16 | date = 2018-10-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801021842/https://heraldodemexico.com.mx/estados/van-10-desgajamientos-por-lluvias-en-hidalgo-afectan-carreteras-y-vialidades/ | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no}}</ref>

=== 美国 ===
10月24日，飓风威拉的残留在[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]和[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]产生暴雨和雷暴<Ref name="TCR" />。当地土壤含水已因过去一个月间降水过多饱和，德克萨斯州东南部的[[加尔维斯顿县|加尔维斯顿县]]接获山洪警报<ref name="Houston">{{cite news | url = https://www.click2houston.com/weather/2018/10/25/hurricane-willa-leftovers-to-bring-rain-to-houston-on-wednesday/ | title = Hurricane Willa Leftovers to Bring Rain to Houston on Wednesday | first1 = Aaron | last1 = Barker | first2 = Eric | last2 = Braate | work = KPRC Click2Houston | date = 2018-10-24 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190421204322/https://www.click2houston.com/weather/how-a-pacific-hurricane-will-impact-houston | archive-date = 2019-04-21 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="drench US states">{{cite web | url = https://edition.cnn.com/2018/10/24/us/hurricane-willa-us-impact-wxc/index.html | title = Willa Will Drench US States and Could Turn into a Nor'easter | first = Holly | last = Yan | publisher = Cable News Network | date = 2018-10-24 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190421204328/https://edition.cnn.com/2018/10/24/us/hurricane-willa-us-impact-wxc/index.html | archive-date = 2019-04-21 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[加尔维斯顿斯科尔斯国际机场|加尔维斯顿斯科尔斯国际机场]]（{{lang|en|Scholes International Airport at Galveston}}）降水达到120毫米<ref name="TCR" />，打破1883年创下的该市日降雨量纪录<ref>{{cite report | page = 12 | format = PDF | publisher = Houston, Texas National Weather Service | url = https://www.weather.gov/media/hgx/climate/summary/October_2018_Regional_Climate_Summary.pdf | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200321141446/https://www.weather.gov/media/hgx/climate/summary/October_2018_Regional_Climate_Summary.pdf | archivedate = 2020-03-21 | deadurl = no | title = October 2018 Regional Climate Summary | accessdate = 2020-09-23}}</ref>。雨水引发山洪，流入沼泽、河道，将街道和部分汽车淹没<ref>{{cite news | title = Coastal Counties Flooded after Heavy Rains from Hurricane Willa Remnants | work = KPRC Click2Houston | url = https://www.click2houston.com/weather/2018/10/25/coastal-counties-flooded-after-heavy-rains-from-hurricane-willa-remnants/ | date = 2018-10-25 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200321141444/https://www.click2houston.com/weather/2018/10/25/coastal-counties-flooded-after-heavy-rains-from-hurricane-willa-remnants/ | archive-date = 2020-03-21 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite report | title = Event: Flash Flood in Arcadia, TX [2018-10-24 18:55 CST-6] | publisher = National Centers for Environmental Information | url = https://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/stormevents/eventdetails.jsp?id=788965 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200518153813/https://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/stormevents/eventdetails.jsp?id=788965 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | series = Storm Events Database | archive-date = 2020-05-18 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。洪水还进入[[德克萨斯州农工大学|德克萨斯州农工大学]][[德克萨斯州农工大学加尔维斯顿分校|加尔维斯顿分校]]的宿舍<ref>{{cite report | title = Event: Flash Flood in Galveston, TX [2018-10-24 18:55 CST-6] | publisher = National Centers for Environmental Information | url = https://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/stormevents/eventdetails.jsp?id=788966 | accessdate = 2020-09-23 | series = Storm Events Database | archive-date = 2020-05-18 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200518154016/https://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/stormevents/eventdetails.jsp?id=788966}}</ref>。

== 善后 ==
墨西哥当局派出包括军人、水手、医生和护士在内的4.5万人协助救灾<ref>{{cite news | last = Suárez | first = Tatiana | title = Tras causar estragos en el pacífico mexicano, Willa se degrada a depresión tropical | url = https://www.france24.com/es/20181024-huracan-willa-degrada-tormenta-tropical | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | work = France 24 | date = 2018-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174541/https://www.france24.com/es/20181024-huracan-willa-degrada-tormenta-tropical | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="milen" />。科利马州、杜兰戈州、哈利斯科州、锡那罗亚州和纳亚里特州启动旨在协调搜救工作和救灾援助的[[DN-III-E计划|DN-III-E计划]]（{{lang|en|DN-III-E Plan}}）。锡那罗亚州库利亚坎（{{lang|es|Culiacán}}）、罗萨里奥（{{lang|es|El Rosario}}）、[[埃斯奎纳帕自治区|埃斯奎纳帕]]、拉克鲁兹伊洛塔（{{lang|es|La Cruz de Elota}}）和马萨特兰自治区约布署1.1万名军人，协助将平民送到四个避难所，该州约1820人分得1400份口粮。军人在蒂卡潘医院修理受损的窗户，并将路上倒塌的树木挪走。杜兰戈州约部署590名军人。262名军人在科利马州监测马拉巴斯科河水位。米却肯州官员动员五百名军人协助灾民。哈利斯科州梅拉克、[[巴亚尔塔港|巴亚尔塔港]]和[[托马特兰|托马特兰]]（{{lang|en|Tomatlán}}）共有154人在108名军人帮助下转移。<ref name="Plan DN-III-E">{{cite news | last = Moya | first = Ricardo | title = Aplica Sedena Plan DN-III-E tras paso de huracán "Willa" en Sinaloa | url = https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/aplica-sedena-plan-dn-iii-e-tras-paso-de-huracan-willa-en-sinaloa | work = El Universal | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | date = 2018-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200527103218/https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/aplica-sedena-plan-dn-iii-e-tras-paso-de-huracan-willa-en-sinaloa | archive-date = 2020-05-27 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Sedena aplica Plan DN-III-E en costa del Pacífico por huracán ‘Willa’ | url = https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/sedena-aplica-plan-dn-iii-e-en-costa-del-pacifico-por-huracan-willa/ | work = Noticieros Televisa | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | date = 2018-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190811140148/https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/sedena-aplica-plan-dn-iii-e-en-costa-del-pacifico-por-huracan-willa/ | archive-date = 2019-08-11 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="morrr" />墨西哥城政府在该市普希金花园（{{lang|en|Pushkin Garden}}）设立食品、清洁用品和卫生用品收集中心<ref>{{cite news | title = Instala gobierno capitalino centro de acopio para apoyar a afectados por “Willa” | url = https://aristeguinoticias.com/3010/mexico/instala-gobierno-capitalino-centro-de-acopio-para-apoyar-a-afectados-por-willa/ | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | work = Aristegui Noticias | date = 2018-10-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174545/https://aristeguinoticias.com/3010/mexico/instala-gobierno-capitalino-centro-de-acopio-para-apoyar-a-afectados-por-willa/ | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。{{lang|en|DN-III-E}}计划在纳亚里特州图斯潘建立社区厨房，[[墨西哥陆军|墨西哥陆军]]在此分配三千份饭菜<ref name="Tuxpan flood" />。墨西哥国家整体家庭发展系统共向飓风影响地区提供1600公吨援助物资，其中包括储藏的食品、镀锌金属板和瓶装水<ref>{{cite news | last = Espinosa | first = Gabriela | title = El paso del Huràcan “Willa” dejó daños por 3 mil 650 millones de pesos en Nayarit | url = https://www.sopitas.com/noticias/huracan-willa-danos-3-mil-650-millones-pesos-nayarit/ | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | work = Sopitas | date = 2018-11-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200730123324/https://www.sopitas.com/noticias/huracan-willa-danos-3-mil-650-millones-pesos-nayarit/ | archive-date = 2020-07-30 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

锡那罗亚州和纳亚里特州启动海洋计划，共计调遣1800名军人、163辆运输工具、八架飞机、15支地面部队、六艘舰船和三套移动厨房。[[墨西哥红十字会|墨西哥红十字会]]向两州提供4.4万公吨物资，其中运至纳亚里特州储藏室的有1.8万公吨，包括一千套卫生用品，另外2.6万公吨运至锡那罗亚州储藏室。此外，锡那罗亚州、纳亚里特州、哈利斯科州和[[瓜納華托州|瓜納華托州]]均开设收集中心。埃斯奎纳帕的罗萨里奥和克里斯托雷（{{lang|es|Cristo Rey}}）共有约178人疏散。军人利用移动厨房在纳亚里特州特夸拉（{{lang|es|Tecuala}}）分发约五百份食物。<ref>{{cite news | last = Mejía | first = Ximena | title = Cruz Roja envía apoyo a damnificados de Nayarit y Sinaloa | url = https://www.excelsior.com.mx/nacional/cruz-roja-envia-apoyo-a-damnificados-de-nayarit-y-sinaloa/1274176 | work = Excelsior | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | date = 2018-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174542/https://www.excelsior.com.mx/nacional/cruz-roja-envia-apoyo-a-damnificados-de-nayarit-y-sinaloa/1274176 | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Moya | first = Ricardo | title = Activan fase de auxilio del Plan Marina en Nayarit y Sinaloa por "Willa" | url = https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/activan-fase-de-auxilio-del-plan-marina-en-nayarit-y-sinaloa-por-willa | work = El Universal | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | date = 2018-10-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200527103209/https://www.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/activan-fase-de-auxilio-del-plan-marina-en-nayarit-y-sinaloa-por-willa | archive-date = 2020-05-27 | deadurl = no}}</ref>图斯潘自治区政府向灾民提供1270公吨食品、水、衣物、药品及其他物资<ref name="ladobe" />。纳亚里特州官员向该州北部受灾最严重的地区派出76辆汽车运载医疗物资<ref name="nay25" />。哈利斯科州民防和消防机构利用水运工具向图斯潘自治区运送物资并评估纳亚里特州所受破坏<ref>{{cite news | title = Protección Civil Jalisco apoya en Nayarit a afectados por ''Willa'' | url = https://www.informador.mx/jalisco/Proteccion-Civil-Jalisco-apoya-en-Nayarit-a-afectados-por-Willa-20181025-0074.html | work = Informador | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | date = 2018-10-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801134344/https://www.informador.mx/jalisco/Proteccion-Civil-Jalisco-apoya-en-Nayarit-a-afectados-por-Willa-20181025-0074.html | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。政府官员下令本是收费公路的墨西哥15{{lang|en|D}}号联邦公路免费通行一周，并为因飓风流离失所的灾民提供110万墨西哥比索（合5.7万美元）损款<ref>{{cite news | first = Myriam | last = Navarro | title = Exitosa colecta para damnificados de Willa olvidados por el gobierno | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | date = 2018-11-25 | work = La Jornada | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181126113032/https://www.jornada.com.mx/2018/11/25/estados/027n3est?partner=rss | url = https://www.jornada.com.mx/2018/11/25/estados/027n3est?partner=rss | archive-date = 2018-11-26 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。墨西哥总检察长办公室向锡那罗亚州和纳亚里特州提供11公吨粮食和半吨药品，并派出四名医生<ref>{{cite news | title = Trasladan 11 toneladas de víveres a Sinaloa y Nayarit por daños causados por huracán ‘Willa’ | url = https://aristeguinoticias.com/3010/mexico/trasladan-11-toneladas-de-viveres-a-sinaloa-y-nayarit-por-danos-causados-por-huracan-willa/ | work = Aristegui Noticias | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | date = 2018-10-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731171327/https://aristeguinoticias.com/3010/mexico/trasladan-11-toneladas-de-viveres-a-sinaloa-y-nayarit-por-danos-causados-por-huracan-willa/ | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[救助儿童会|救助儿童会]]（{{lang|en|Save the Children}}）向纳亚里特州儿童提供八百套卫生用品，还开设17家餐饮设施，为近三千儿童提供饮食，但位于博斯克岛（{{lang|es|Isla del Bosque}}）、埃斯奎纳帕和蒂卡潘（{{lang|es|Teacapán}}）的设施因供电不足关闭<ref>{{cite news | title = Huracán Willa: pequeñas comunidades de Sinaloa continúan afectadas | url = https://www.elsoldetijuana.com.mx/mexico/sociedad/huracan-willa-pequenas-comunidades-de-sinaloa-continuan-afectadas-2379372.html | work = El Sol de Tijuana | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | date = 2018-10-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731171337/https://www.elsoldetijuana.com.mx/mexico/sociedad/huracan-willa-pequenas-comunidades-de-sinaloa-continuan-afectadas-2379372.html | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

据墨西哥石油公司提供的消息，风暴过后瓜納華托州汽油短缺，估计主要原因是基础设施受损及偷油行为增多。部分港口无法卸油，偷油行为还导致部分运油管道关闭，其中图拉至[[萨拉曼卡|萨拉曼卡]]段管道因偷油贼破坏而需封闭维修。<ref>{{cite news | title = Robo de combustible deja con desabasto de gasolina a Guanajuato | url = https://lopezdoriga.com/nacional/robo-de-combustible-deja-con-desabasto-de-gasolina-a-guanajuato/ | work = Lopez-Doriga | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | date = 2018-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801021838/https://lopezdoriga.com/nacional/robo-de-combustible-deja-con-desabasto-de-gasolina-a-guanajuato/ | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>

锡那罗亚州州长[[基里诺·奥尔达斯·科珀尔|基里诺·奥尔达斯·科珀尔]]（{{lang|es|Quirino Ordaz Coppel}}）宣布七个自治区进入紧急状态<ref>{{cite news | last = Ibarra | first = Aarón | date = 2018-10-24 | title = Descarta Quirino Ordaz muertes por paso de huracán 'Willa' | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | work = Ríodoce | url = https://riodoce.mx/2018/10/24/descarta-quirino-ordaz-muertes-por-paso-de-huracan-willa/ | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190421204325/https://riodoce.mx/noticias/descarta-quirino-ordaz-muertes-por-paso-de-huracan-willa | archive-date = 2019-04-21 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。11月5日，[[锡那罗亚多拉多斯队|锡那罗亚多拉多斯队]]教练[[迭戈·马拉多纳|迭戈·马拉多纳]]主持慈善晚宴，为威拉和[[2018年第19E号热带低气压|第19E号热带低气压]]的灾民提供财政援助<ref>{{cite news | title = Maradona apoya a los damnificados por el huracán Willa | url = https://www.esto.com.mx/397203-ultimas-noticias-liga-mx-ascenso-mx-huracan-willa-sinaloa-397203/ | website = Esto | accessdate = 2020-06-20 | date = 2018-11-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190105033029/https://www.esto.com.mx/397203-ultimas-noticias-liga-mx-ascenso-mx-huracan-willa-sinaloa-397203/ | archive-date = 2019-01-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

墨西哥国家民防协调会将纳亚里特州阿卡波内塔、华吉科里、德尔纳亚尔（{{lang|es|Del Nayar}}、特夸拉、[[罗萨莫拉达|罗萨莫拉达]]（{{lang|es|Rosamorada}}）、[[鲁伊斯_(纳亚里特州)|鲁伊斯]]（{{lang|es|Ruiz}}）、[[圣地亚哥伊克斯昆特拉|圣地亚哥伊克斯昆特拉]]（{{lang|es|Santiago Ixcuintla}}）和图斯潘列为灾区<ref>{{cite news | last = Arellano | first = Salvador | title = Declaran zona de desastre a 8 municipios de Nayarit por huracán ‘Willa’ | url = https://www.msn.com/es-mx/noticias/mexico/declaran-zona-de-desastre-a-8-municipios-de-nayarit-por-hurac%C3%A1n-%E2%80%98willa%E2%80%99/ar-BBPbsDI#page=2 | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | work = MSN | date = 2018-10-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174545/https://www.msn.com/es-mx/noticias/mexico/declaran-zona-de-desastre-a-8-municipios-de-nayarit-por-hurac%25C3%25A1n-%25E2%2580%2598willa%25E2%2580%2599/ar-BBPbsDI#page=2 | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。另据报导，锡那罗亚州[[埃斯奎纳帕德伊达尔戈|埃斯奎纳帕自治区]]两千余户家庭在飓风过去半年后仍然在塑料棚中生活。此外，市长埃米特·索托·格雷夫（{{lang|en|Emmet Soto Grave}}）称，上届政府汇报灾情时存在多处违规。10月23至28日，市政府统计的受损房屋数量仅144套，但实际受风暴影响的超过两千。[[墨西哥总统|墨西哥总统]][[洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔|洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔]]派联邦官员前往调查，发现公路、教育设施和旅游景点的破坏情况报告存在更多不尽不实之处。<ref>{{cite news | first = Adriana | last = Carlos | title = En Sinaloa, aún hay más de 2 mil viviendo en casas provisionales por 'Willa' | url = https://www.milenio.com/estados/sinaloa-2-mil-viviendo-casas-provisionales-willa | work = Milenio | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | date = 2019-03-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200911044958/https://www.milenio.com/estados/sinaloa-2-mil-viviendo-casas-provisionales-willa | archive-date = 2020-09-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>气旋消散后的一个月里，墨西哥国家水资源委员会称[[巴鲁阿特河|巴鲁阿特河]]（{{lang|en|Baluarte River}}）的[[铬|铬]]、[[汞|汞]]和[[镍|镍]]含量大幅上升<ref>{{cite news | first = Sibely | last = Cañedo | title = Tras el Huracán Willa, suben niveles de metales en río Baluarte | archive-date = 2019-04-20 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.noroeste.com.mx/publicaciones/view/huracan-willa-azoto-en-el-sur-y-niveles-de-cromo-niquel-y-mercurio-subieron-en-rio-baluarte-1159453 | work = Noroeste | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | date = 2019-03-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190420213713/https://www.noroeste.com.mx/publicaciones/view/huracan-willa-azoto-en-el-sur-y-niveles-de-cromo-niquel-y-mercurio-subieron-en-rio-baluarte-1159453 }}</ref>。威拉产生的强烈阵风令各地芒果园损失惨重，产量大跌五成至七五成，相当于损失七万公吨芒果或1.33万公顷果园绝收<ref>{{cite news | title = Huracán 'Willa' golpeó producción de mango en Sinaloa | url = https://www.nnc.mx/categoria/sinaloa/huracan--willa--golpeo-produccion-de-mango-en-sinaloa/1559960245 | work = NNC.mx | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | date = 2019-06-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731171328/https://www.nnc.mx/articulo/sinaloa/huracan--willa--golpeo-produccion-de-mango-en-sinaloa/1559960245 | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Rochín | first = Victor | title = Daños por el huracán Willa, provocan caída en la producción de mango en el sur de Sinaloa | url = https://tvpacifico.mx/noticias/234151-danos-por-el-huracan-willa-provocan-caida-en-la-produccion-de-mango-en-el-sur-de-sinaloa | work = Televisoras del Pacífico | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | date = 2019-07-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731171328/https://tvpacifico.mx/noticias/234151-danos-por-el-huracan-willa-provocan-caida-en-la-produccion-de-mango-en-el-sur-de-sinaloa | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，导致至少1200户农民需要贷款<ref>{{cite news | first = Claudia | last = Cabanillas | title = Precios del mango se verán 'castigados' en Sinaloa | url = https://www.elsoldemazatlan.com.mx/finanzas/precios-del-mango-se-veran-castigados-en-sinaloa-2981404.html | work = El Sol de Mazatlán | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | date = 2019-01-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174555/https://www.elsoldemazatlan.com.mx/finanzas/precios-del-mango-se-veran-castigados-en-sinaloa-2981404.html | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。马萨特兰市长向埃斯奎纳帕提供两台起重机和三辆倾卸卡车，并派遣60名工人前往<ref name="Support" />。风暴过去数月后，罗萨里奥部分社区依然面临饮用水短缺<ref name="Rosario" />。

受圣佩德罗河与阿卡波內塔河沿线洪灾影响，风暴过后第一周至少有18万人缺乏食品且无法同外界联络<ref name="Shrimp" />。部分居民家中满是河泥，只能完全自力清理<ref>{{cite news | title = Damnificados de Nayarit viven bajo el lodo tras paso de ‘Willa’ | url = https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/damnificados-de-nayarit-viven-bajo-el-lodo-tras-paso-de-willa/ | work = Noticieros Televisa | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | date = 2018-11-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200321120640/https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/damnificados-de-nayarit-viven-bajo-el-lodo-tras-paso-de-willa/ | archive-date = 2020-03-21 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。纳亚里特州灾民在飓风过后一个半月里都只得到救灾援助组织的帮助，感觉仿佛“被政府抛弃”。图斯潘的学校设施受损，所以长期停课。阿卡波内塔小镇桑多瓦莱斯（{{lang|es|Los Sandovales}}）毁于一旦，大量居民无家可归<ref>{{cite news | title = Nayarit, paralizado por falta de ayuda tras paso de huracán ‘Willa’ | url = https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/nayarit-paralizado-por-falta-de-ayuda-tras-paso-de-huracan-willa/ | work = Noticieros Televisa | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | date = 2018-12-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200408083928/https://noticieros.televisa.com/ultimas-noticias/nayarit-paralizado-por-falta-de-ayuda-tras-paso-de-huracan-willa/ | archive-date = 2020-04-08 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = TRAGEDIA: Poderoso huracán “Willa” destruye un pueblo de México | url = https://laverdadnoticias.com/mexico/TRAGEDIA-Poderoso-huracan-Willa-destruye-un-pueblo-de-Mexico-20181102-0054.html | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | work = La Verdad Noticias | date = 2018-11-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200911045630/https://laverdadnoticias.com/mexico/TRAGEDIA-Poderoso-huracan-Willa-destruye-un-pueblo-de-Mexico-20181102-0054.html | archive-date = 2020-09-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。灾难过后几周里，纳亚里特州政府宣布政府已经破产，无法为重建提供资金<ref>{{cite news | title = Nayarit, entre la crisis financiera y los daños de "Willa" | url = https://lasillarota.com/estados/nayarit-entre-la-crisis-financiera-y-los-danos-de-willa-nayarit-deuda-publica-huracan-willa/258512 | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | work = La Silla Rota | date = 2018-11-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200911041859/https://lasillarota.com/estados/nayarit-entre-la-crisis-financiera-y-los-danos-de-willa-nayarit-deuda-publica-huracan-willa/258512 | archive-date = 2020-09-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="Nayarit bankrupt" />。2019年，墨西哥政府宣布为纳亚里特州受灾自治区重建提供2.5亿墨西哥比索（合1040万美元），计划从二月开始重建<ref name="Govt Contribution">{{cite news | title = ¡Por fin!, Reconstrucción de Nayarit tras huracán Willa inicia en febrero | url = https://vallartaindependiente.com/2019/01/28/por-fin-reconstruccion-de-nayarit-tras-huracan-willa-inicia-en-febrero/ | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | work = Vallarta Independiente | date = 2019-01-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200911052239/https://vallartaindependiente.com/2019/01/28/por-fin-reconstruccion-de-nayarit-tras-huracan-willa-inicia-en-febrero/ | archive-date = 2020-09-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。联邦救济基金共向图斯潘、罗萨莫拉达、特夸拉、阿卡波内塔和华吉科里拨款2319万墨西哥比索（合96.1万美元），当地533户居民各获得三万墨西哥比索（合1250美元）用于修复房屋。两名联邦官员向另外30户住房完全被毁的居民各提供12万墨西哥比索（合五千美元）。<ref>{{cite news | last = Navarro | first = Myriam | title = Entregan hasta 120 mil pesos a familias damnificadas por ‘Willa’ | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | work = La Jornada | date = 2019-03-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801134348/https://www.jornada.com.mx/ultimas/estados/2019/03/28/entregan-recursos-por-120-mil-pesos-a-damnificados-por-2018willa2019-878.html | archivedate = 2019-08-01 | url = https://www.jornada.com.mx/ultimas/estados/2019/03/28/entregan-recursos-por-120-mil-pesos-a-damnificados-por-2018willa2019-878.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>墨西哥政府还为公路、桥梁、学校和医院等公共基础设施重建拨款20亿墨西哥比索（合8360万美元）<ref name="Govt Contribution" />。估计纳亚里特州公共基础设施的修复成本约为22亿墨西哥比索（合9200万美元）<ref name="Nayarit Infrastructure" />，清理该州交通要道淤泥的开支估计就要3900万墨西哥比索（合160万美元）<ref>{{cite news | last = Méndez | first = Karla | title = Sedatu realiza censo de viviendas dañadas por ‘Willa’ en Nayarit | url = https://www.excelsior.com.mx/nacional/sedatu-realiza-censo-de-viviendas-danadas-por-willa-en-nayarit/1278509 | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | work = Excelsior | date = 2018-11-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801134354/https://www.excelsior.com.mx/nacional/sedatu-realiza-censo-de-viviendas-danadas-por-willa-en-nayarit/1278509 | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。墨西哥国家级百货公司[[科珀尔|科珀尔]]（{{lang|es|Coppel}}）从墨西哥政府获得6600万墨西哥比索（合280万美元），用于向4400户家庭各提供价值1.5万墨西哥比索（合625美元）的家具和家电优惠卷<ref name="Nayarit Infrastructure">{{cite news | last = Cancino | first = Karina | title = Coppel recibe 66 mdp por programa de apoyo para damnificados del huracán 'Willa' | url = https://www.elfinanciero.com.mx/economia/coppel-recibe-66-mdp-por-programa-de-apoyo-para-damnificados-del-huracan-willa-en-nayarit | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | work = El Financiero | publisher = Bloomberg | date = 2018-12-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190801134344/https://www.elfinanciero.com.mx/economia/coppel-recibe-66-mdp-por-programa-de-apoyo-para-damnificados-del-huracan-willa-en-nayarit | archive-date = 2019-08-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。由于丰登资源不足，锡那罗亚州灾民只能自掏腰包重建家园。该州向灾民提供价值两百万墨西哥比索（合10.1万美元）但已经腐烂的床单，同时允许灾民获取储藏室内的物资，目的是换取小企业主价值1800至一万墨西哥比索（合90至500美元）的赞助信。<ref>{{cite news | title = Sinaloa asegura que superó contingencia por Willa; datos de reconstrucción no son públicos, acusan ONG | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.animalpolitico.com/2018/11/sinaloa-emergencia-willa-reconstruccion/ | work = Animal Politico | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | date = 2018-11-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174546/https://www.animalpolitico.com/2018/11/sinaloa-emergencia-willa-reconstruccion/ }}</ref>锡那罗亚州官员声称，丰登可能需要三年才能凑足修复工程所需资金<ref>{{cite news | last = Gamboa Parra | first = Jose Luis | title = Sinaloa tendrá que esperar tres años para recibir el apoyo de Fonden | url = https://www.tribuna.com.mx/mexico/Sinaloa-tendra-que-esperar-tres-anos-para-recibir-el-apoyo-de-Fonden-20181103-0009.html | work = Tribuna | accessdate = 2019-07-31 | date = 2018-11-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174542/https://www.tribuna.com.mx/mexico/Sinaloa-tendra-que-esperar-tres-anos-para-recibir-el-apoyo-de-Fonden-20181103-0009.html | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = yes}}</ref>。丰登已授权为飓风威拉的灾后重建提供总额8470万墨西哥比索（合430万美元）资金，但这笔钱一直不知所踪，风暴过去几个月后，修复工作仍未开始<ref name="Rosario" />。洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔总统到包括马萨特兰市在内的锡那罗亚州多地视察后，丰登又为埃斯奎纳帕和罗萨里奥提供5.1亿墨西哥比索（合2390万美元）用于救灾<ref>{{cite news | last = Ibarra | first = Maria | title = Fonden entregaría 510 mdp para reconstrucción del sur | url = https://www.debate.com.mx/sinaloa/sinaloa/Fonden-entregaria-510-mdp-para-reconstruccion-del-sur-20190131-0006.html | work = Debate | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | date = 2019-01-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174541/https://www.debate.com.mx/sinaloa/sinaloa/Fonden-entregaria-510-mdp-para-reconstruccion-del-sur-20190131-0006.html | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Recursos llegarán, pero tomará tiempo: AMLO a damnificados de Willa en Nayarit | url = https://aristeguinoticias.com/2501/mexico/recursos-llegaran-pero-tomara-tiempo-amlo-a-damnificados-de-willa-en-nayarit/ | accessdate = 2020-09-24 | work = Aristegui Noticias | date = 2019-01-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731174542/https://aristeguinoticias.com/2501/mexico/recursos-llegaran-pero-tomara-tiempo-amlo-a-damnificados-de-willa-en-nayarit/ | archive-date = 2019-07-31 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

